  <trk>
    <name>INN-L1 — Timmelsjoch &amp; Dolomites Chain Weekend Loop — Day 2</name>
    <desc>Deploy from INN and ride into the Timmelsjoch &amp; Dolomites Chain. Hit Kühtai Pass — 2017m and Sölden — 1368m. Loop back to INN over a packed 2–3 day weekend escape. No highways, just curves and elevation.</desc>
